{"tid":2312054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國航天局：成功在月球插國旗　","createTime":"2020-12-04T14:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T07:19:44.000Z","uid":2104,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0a4b1227417ae6675ca0a14ba715caa36eb978","tid":2312054,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"網民：新聞相片極似CG圖<br />\n<br />\n中國在周二（24日）成功將嫦娥五號升空，而據最新消息指，嫦娥五號在周四（3 日）成功將攜帶月球土壤樣品的上升器送到預定環月軌道，並在該工作期間，實現了月面國旗展開，即在月球表面成功展示中國國旗。<br />\n <br />\n據中國數家傳媒報導，國家航天局在 12 月 3 日 23 時 10 分指，嫦娥五號上升器工作約 6 分鐘後，成功將攜帶土壤樣品的上升器從月球表面起飛，送入到預定環月軌道將樣本轉移到返回器。據指，在上升器點火起飛前，其在月球上實現中國首次月面國旗展開，成功在月球表面獨立展示一面「真正的中國國旗」，而非像嫦娥三號、四號般，只展示在月球車上噴塗的國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pw1tCj9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPw1tCj9.png&h=2f9aa952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有中國報導指「照片」中的國旗在陽光的照耀下，呈現出一抹鮮艷的「中國紅」<br />\n<br />\n不過就有不少網民指，中央電視台提供的相片極似 CG 電腦合成圖片，但在中央電視台與多間中國傳媒在報導此新聞時，未有註明圖片是 CG 圖，在某些報導縮小圖片的情況下，圖片極像真。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8u0NSTP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8u0NSTP.jpg&h=d246fbd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲但有不少網民指中央電視台發佈的圖片極似 CG 合成電腦圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuDzyd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuDzyd9.jpg&h=68a8962a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7m6Jrza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7m6Jrza.jpg&h=96f98ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzaNTea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzaNTea.jpg&h=ab55c256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n航天科工集團航天三江九部研製團隊表示，月球的環境會令普通旗幟在短時間內褪色甚至分解，故其為了是次的月面國旗展開進行了一段長時間的研究，只在選材上已花費超過 1 年，再通過熱匹配性、耐高低溫、防靜電、防月球塵埃等試驗，才選定某新型複合材料，製成了嫦娥五號展示的國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7VNTes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7VNTes.jpg&h=92d43b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，國家航天局以及研製團隊均未有明言，該旗幟選用的複合材料到底為何，亦未有多加解釋如何使得該旗幟符合月球環境，只交代國旗展示系統由月面國旗、壓緊釋放裝置、展開機構三部分組成，不少網民均對其真確性相當懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/04/change-5-3/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2Fchange-5-3%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=802cdd0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/04/change-5-3/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"26c7c051061be99fa19fdff3e05525080f87315e","tid":2312054,"uid":155818,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"支旗咁撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32adac025645e866008d42f40b1ef16526802fa9","tid":2312054,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"太空軍is watch you"},{"pid":"2b87e75d5897e2f433fdf9d13e434be18b45ca01","tid":2312054,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32adac025645e866008d42f40b1ef16526802fa9","tid":2312054,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"太空軍is watch you"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"watching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa69d109785183795536c694bf5ad0f570a84aa","tid":2312054,"uid":74171,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26c7c051061be99fa19fdff3e05525080f87315e","tid":2312054,"uid":155818,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"支旗咁撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"成功在月球<span class=\"red\">模型</span>插縮水版國旗"},{"pid":"cf93db2bb58cce6ae6d834218d7885e634842588","tid":2312054,"uid":61745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"勢質CG圖"},{"pid":"20f940bbc5f9c6142c38dc8ec8455d289e74763b","tid":2312054,